latestPosts.caption:
YOUR GIRL JUST GOT FEATURED IN HINDUSTAN TIMES! 🗞️🧿
A dedicated feature recognizing my work is a huge deal for a girl who has struggled from ground zero and is proudly self-made.

Growing up, I could have never imagined having a dedicated feature in a national newspaper read by 180 million people. When I was 8 years old in school, I attended HT PACE workshops organized by @hindustantimes , which were my favorite part of schooling. I basically grew up reading the newspaper and admiring—respecting—those who made it there.

Never, EVER did I imagine I would grow up to be one of them!
To more wins, and HELPING MORE WOMEN - Dress Better 💖♥️
